---
import Landing from "../layouts/Landing.astro";
---

<Landing title="Terms of Service — Drobu" description="Terms of Service for Drobu clipboard manager for macOS.">
  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <a href="/clipboard-history/" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors mb-8 inline-block">&larr; Back to home</a>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-sm max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <p><strong class="text-text-primary">Last updated:</strong> March 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">1. Subscription</h2>
      <p>
        Drobu is offered as a monthly subscription at $9.99 USD per month. New subscribers receive a 14-day free trial. Your payment method will be charged automatically at the end of the trial period and on each monthly renewal date thereafter.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">2. Free Trial</h2>
      <p>
        The 14-day free trial requires a valid payment method. If you do not cancel before the trial ends, your subscription will automatically convert to a paid monthly subscription at $9.99/month. You will not be charged during the trial period.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">3. Cancellation</h2>
      <p>
        You may cancel your subscription at any time. After cancellation, you will continue to have access to Drobu until the end of your current billing period. No partial refunds are provided for unused time within a billing period.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">4. Refunds</h2>
      <p>
        If you are not satisfied with Drobu, contact us within 7 days of your first charge for a full refund. Refunds for subsequent billing periods are handled on a case-by-case basis.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">5. License</h2>
      <p>
        Your subscription grants you a personal, non-transferable license to use Drobu on your macOS devices. You may not redistribute, reverse-engineer, or resell the software.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">6. Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        Drobu is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We are not liable for any data loss, damages, or issues arising from the use of the software. Your clipboard data is stored locally on your device and is your responsibility.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">7. Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of Drobu after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms. Material changes will be communicated via the email address associated with your subscription.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">8. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about these terms, email <a href="mailto:support@drobu.app" class="text-accent hover:underline">support@drobu.app</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Landing>
